<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532099514109-7d2d71629d82?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80);">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Louez le rêve de vos rêves</h1>
    <p>Ne subissez plus vos rêves, prenez le contrôle</p>
    <a class="btn btn-light button" href="dreams">Rêver</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Nos rêves les plus populaires </h1>
  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4">
